<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khatvei gitloh kawlbut in ka tanga,
 Suohchak guo mahleng suokcha zolo;
 Mahleh suohchakna lopi ka nei tai,
 Isun ka kawlbuh ei phelsak tai.

[V2]
 Suohchakna lopi, Suohchakna maktak,
 Gitloh kawlbuta mau kit talo;
 Ei pawtsakpa lopi, Isu ahi,
 Kumsawtin A mah keia hina.

[V3]
 2. Awhchak, hawtna, kiniel leh kinakna,
 Kiletsakna leh kideihnahaw;
 Khawvel thildeih ka hin hihnuomlo cheng,
 Sa ut leh deih apat suohchakna.

[V4]
 3. Kisaktheih leh gitloh nawpsaknan pat,
 Sum-le-pai, neihzawh utna apat;
 Lungnat, lung gilo apat suohchakna,
 Suohchakna lopi, nawpna lopi.

[V5]
 4. Lauhna, thawmhauhna apat suohchakna,
 Lungkham, lungzin apat suohchakna;
 Tanpa Krista ah suohchakna a um,
 Ka kawlbuh cheng phel Amah ahi.</lyrics>
<title>GLORIOUS FREEDOM</title>
</song>